1.0.name: wordpress/emphaino
1.0.description: The word 'emphaino' means "to show in, to exhibit;" (en, "in," phaino, "to cause to shine"). Let your thoughts, your work, your art shine with Emphaino, a modern, responsive WordPress theme. Clean design, emphasis on content. Customization through the interactive WP customizer interface. Compatible with WordPress 3.5 and above.
